   6:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_gpio.c ****   *          This file provides firmware functions to manage the following
   7:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_gpio.c ****   *          functionalities of the General Purpose Input/Output (GPIO) peripheral:
